Darkfate barely avoided the attak and after that he shot against

spinator flew in his beast mode through the air avoiding beams from
> the sweeps as he grabbed the missile that he had hidden earlier. He
> lifted it and then looked for a important looking enemy. Spotting
> Darkfate he flew in for the attack dropping the missile from above 
and
